WEBVTT

11:50.454 --> 11:54.334
<b><i>At every turn, one false step,</i></b>

11:54.334 --> 11:58.464
<b><i>and I could've found myself
in that same situation.</i></b>

11:59.264 --> 12:01.884
<b><i>I was lucky enough to remain a human,</i></b>

12:02.224 --> 12:07.354
<b><i>but there could've been a future
in which we were both demons.</i></b>
